cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "PhiSpace ST: a platform-agnostic method to identify cell states in spatial transcriptomics studies"
message: "If you use this software, please cite both the Cell Reports Methods paper and this archived software release."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Mao
    given-names: Jiadong
